        <TR>
          <TD bgColor=#e8e8e8 class=view align=middle vAlign=center><B>작성자</B></FONT></TD>
					<TD bgColor=white class=view>&nbsp; &nbsp; <font color=#010080><a href='mailto:jymh@moneytoday.co.kr'>알렉스 윤</a> 특파원 &nbsp; | &nbsp; 05/18 09:25 &nbsp; | &nbsp; 조회 334 &nbsp; &nbsp;</font></TD></TR>
